{"tid":1117822,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"19歲妹夢遊中遭性侵　異物入體瞬間驚醒","createTime":"2019-04-21T03:43:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-21T06:42:06.000Z","uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"fac3a7d68aa6c7a5a6dec11f1a02110fb1cf69e9","tid":1117822,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T03:43:50.000Z","msg":"19歲女夢遊亂晃，遭23歲室友性侵。<br />\n<br />\n據《每日郵報》報導，英國23歲男子艾德瓦利(Jordan Adewale)，涉嫌在2017年2月性侵19歲室友，當時這名19歲女子睡著後夢遊，走到住處的廚房，艾德瓦利看到後趁機襲擊她，遭擊後女子立刻醒過來並打電話報警，雖然艾德瓦利否認犯行，但是經驗傷後確定艾德瓦利的確有性侵。<br />\n<br />\n泰晤士谷(Thames Valley)警察巴茲利(Richard Bazeley)說，「艾德瓦利為了自己的性慾，襲擊一名夢遊者，並且在她沒有意識的時候強姦了她，陪審團不相信他的辯解，被判犯了強姦罪」、「我要感謝受害者在面臨出庭的勇氣，並向所有證人表示感謝」，艾德瓦利將於4月26日判刑。（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.tenor.com/images/c2a38f18df6102833b3cd194649ac252/tenor.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.tenor.com%2Fimages%2Fc2a38f18df6102833b3cd194649ac252%2Ftenor.gif&h=0d930f08&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d337699f602f0827d5cba70a4db78f9de7e30886","tid":1117822,"uid":19527,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T03:44:46.000Z","msg":"英國咁冷門既"},{"pid":"3fae4d3b0bc8c043b29397830522e438f4c3e9a9","tid":1117822,"uid":229789,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T06:19:09.000Z","msg":"估錯地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52e370be6064824dd84363458359c0690af1df5a","tid":1117822,"uid":76310,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T06:21:32.000Z","msg":"爆大冷"},{"pid":"fbfd8ae218cea9bd8249e0089f746603045fa84b","tid":1117822,"uid":132262,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T06:33:41.000Z","msg":"A3 其他冷門"},{"pid":"614e9bf64b697ac78bb279c9d02336f5e53cd72f","tid":1117822,"uid":9193,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T06:36:30.000Z","msg":"以為中國台灣"},{"pid":"51320e2b68c46078bc577a68c00c81f38d508ee9","tid":1117822,"uid":22553,"like":0,"dislik